features.text:
A raffle. I have hidden 3
 swords in the world.
 A Silver one a Gold 
and a Diamond.
 If you find one. 
You will get a present.
The first place is a dragon
 and a head. 
The second place is a turtle. 
The third place is a pair of shoes.
GOOD LUCK.
if you find, write me on twitter: Gentnerramon- Elaleman
